Git repo for storing configuration files (.vimrc, .tmux.conf and .zshrc)
Required software:
                    -Vim
                    -curl
                    -tmux
                    -screen (for arduino serial monitor)
                    -zsh
                    -ohmyzsh
                    -python
                    -cmake
                    -thefuck(optional)
                    -https://github.com/zsh-users/zsh-autosuggestions
                        -git clone https://github.com/zsh-users/zsh-autosuggestions ${ZSH_CUSTOM:-~/.oh-my-zsh/custom}/plugins/zsh-autosuggestion


** Run :PlugInstall in vim to update plugins
** After installing all Vim plugins, exit vim and execute 
    'python ~/.vim/plugged/YouCompleteMe/install.py --clang-completer'
